                                <condition>
                                    <p>The manuscript is a fragment of a once larger codex, the
                                        leaves are worn and blackened due to their former use as
                                        binding, especially ff. 4r and 5v have suffered; various
                                        minor damages.</p>
                                </condition>
                            </supportDesc>
